<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - E-Voting System</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        
        body {
            background-image: url('indian-flag-design-made-with-in-wave-style-vector-4593321.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            height: 100vh;
            color: white;
        }

       
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            cursor: pointer; 
        }

        .logo div {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 30px;
            border: 5px solid black;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
        }

       
        .right ul {
            display: flex;
            gap: 34px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .right ul li {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .right ul li a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .right ul li a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        .right ul li img {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .hamburger-menu {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .hamburger-menu div {
            width: 30px;
            height: 5px;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .menu-dropdown {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 10px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 60px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
        }

        .menu-dropdown a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
        }

        .menu-dropdown a:hover {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
        }

        
        .toll-free-number {
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .notification-panel {
            position: fixed;
            top: 150px;
            right: 10px;
            width: 300px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 999;
            animation: float 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
        }

        .notification-panel h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px; 
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .notification {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .notification:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .moving-text {
            display: inline-block;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: moveText 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes moveText {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(100%);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .right {
                display: none;
            }

            .hamburger-menu {
                display: flex;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">
                
                <a href="login.html">
                    <img src="unnamed.png" alt="E-Voting Logo">
                </a>
                <div>Welcome For E-Voting</div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/"><span>Home</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/register"><span>Register</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login"><span>Vote</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/support"><span>Support</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/"><span>About us</span></a></li>
                    <li><span>Toll-free: <strong>Dummy no</strong></span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="hamburger-menu" onclick="toggleMenu()">
                <div></div>
                <div></div>
                <div></div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="menu-dropdown" id="menuDropdown">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/register">Register</a>
        <a href="/login">Vote</a>
        <a href="/support">Support</a>
        <a href="/">About us</a>
    </div>

    <div class="notification-panel" id="notificationPanel">
        <h2>Election Updates</h2>
        <div class="notification">
            <strong>Election Registration Deadline:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nostrum, libero
        </div>
        <div class="notification">
            <strong>Voting Begins Soon:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Reprehenderit, earum.
        </div>
        <div class="notification">
            <strong>Election Results:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Et, officiis.
        </div>
        <div class="notification">
            <strong>ID Update:</strong> Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Reiciendis amet maxime consequuntur molestiae dicta at!
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="moving-text">
            It's not enough to just want change... You have to make a change by voting.
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        
        function toggleMenu() {
            const menuDropdown = document.getElementById('menuDropdown');
            menuDropdown.style.display = menuDropdown.style.display === 'flex' ? 'none' : 'flex';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
